{# ===== How it works (Scan → Map → Build → Polish) ===================== #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--center">How it works</span>
      <h2 class="section__title">A simple way to go from idea to live</h2>
      <p class="section__lead">
        We start by looking, for free, before anyone talks money.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ol class="grid grid--4">
      <li class="step" data-reveal>
        <span class="step__num">1</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Scan</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We review your current site and tell you plainly what’s helping and what’s in the way.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <span class="step__num">2</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Plan</h3>
        <p class="step__text">We agree on the smallest set of changes that will make the biggest difference.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        <span class="step__num">3</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Build</h3>
        <p class="step__text">
          We design and build the site, with booking and chat wired in, and keep you posted as we go.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="step" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <span class="step__num">4</span>
        <h3 class="step__title">Polish</h3>
        <p class="step__text">We tune the copy, speed, and follow-ups after launch until it’s pulling its weight.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div class="btn-row btn-row--center mt-7" data-reveal>
      <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="about.html">See how we work</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

